maml:description.maml:para: Creates a new Logic App in the azure resource group.

The New-AzureRmLogicApp cmdlet creates an Azure Logic App and returns an object that represents the Workflow. Use this cmdlet to create a new Logic App. A Logic App is a collection of actions or triggers defined in Logic App definition. You can create a Logic App with a name, location, Logic App definition, and resource group name.
